    $config[&#39;sess_time_to_update&#39;] = 300;
    $config[&#39;sess_regenerate_destroy&#39;] = FALSE;

You need set the folder path for your session files. To set the folder path you need to set the value of `$config[&#39;sess_save_path&#39;]`which is currently set to `NULL`. You can set the value as below:

    $config[&#39;sess_save_path&#39;] = APPPATH . &#39;cache&#39;;

I am using the cache folder your can use any folder you want but make sure that folder has permission.

